data.description: Welcome to 21363 Maple Harvest Lane featuring an excellent floor plan with 4 large bedrooms, custom wall mouldings throughout home, loft area above your master bedroom that can be used for a nursery, office, or your dream closet (you can also close it off to make it a 5th bedroom), an electric fireplace in master bedroom for the ultimate relaxation, and no backyard neighbors for the privacy you need! No carpet in main areas for easy maintenance, recently replaced flooring throughout second floor, newly replaced back door, upgraded ceiling fans, upgraded light fixtures, kitchen light can be controlled from phone app. The home also has plenty of spacious closets for storage. It is the perfect home for someone looking to have more space but still live in a home that feels cozy and has excellent curb appeal! Schedule your showing today!
